songs.title: Sweet F’in Love
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
You give me that sweet, sweet f'in love
La-la-la-la-la-la-la

Sweet, sighs
Sweet, sighs

[Hook]
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
You give me that sweet, sweet f'in love
La-la-la-la-la-la-la

[Break]
Break it down
Like when it's real quiet
And there's nobody else but me and you
And you can hear everything I'm thinking, even when I don't say it
This life is so sweet in here
We should just go in there, I don't care
Wherever we are, it's like, it doesn't even matter, anywhere
'Cause I take you

[Hook]
Sweet, sweet f'in love
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
I'm talkin' 'bout sweet, sweet f'in love
My baby give me sweet, sweet f'in love

[Outro]
Ah-la-la-la-la-la, la-la-la-la-la-la-la
La-la-la-la-la-la-la, la-la-la-la-la-la-la
La-la-la-la-la-la-la, la-la-la-la-la-la-love
Talkin' bout sweet sweet-weet-weet-weet-weet-weet-sweet fuckin' love, oh yeah, ohhh
Hahaha, you know what I mean

[Produced by KAYTRANADA]
